flowchart LR
  R[Requester creates and submits request] --> A1[Approval step 1: pending]
  A1 -->|atomic activation| A2[Approval step 2: waiting → pending]
  A2 --> S1[Internal signer 1]
  S1 --> S2[Internal signer 2 / External OTP signer]
  S2 --> O[Artifact outbox]
  O --> W[Worker and PDF generation]
  W --> ST[Local storage or S3/MinIO]
  ST --> C[Hash/metadata persisted: Completed]
  C --> D[Authorized final PDF download]
  A1 -->|reject| RS[Reject / resubmit]
  A2 -->|reject| RS
  W -->|failure| F[artifact_failed]
  F -->|authorized retry| O
